#. type: multicols*
#: sections/introduction.tex:7
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{2}\n"
"\\pagetarget{Heroes of Might and Magic III}{\\textbf{Heroes of Might and Magic III: The Board Game}} is a tactical strategy RPG board game for 1--3 players using the core box set, or more when using expansions.  % no-check-caps\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{2}\n"
"\\pagetarget{Heroes of Might and Magic III}{\\textbf{魔法门之英雄无敌III：桌面游戏}}是一款战术策略RPG桌面游戏，使用核心游戏时可支持1-3名玩家，加入扩展时可支持更多玩家。  % no-check-caps\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/introduction.tex:19
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\textbf{Notice}: In this rule book, game and component terms are Capitalized.\n"
"\\textbf{Bold text} is used to draw attention to important rules.\n"
"\\textit{Italicization} is used for gameplay examples.\n"
"\\pagelink{Heroes of Might and Magic III}{Brown colored hyperlinks} will take you to other parts of the rule book.\n"
"Names of specific cards have a \\textcolor{goldenbrown}{\\textbf{°}} appended to them, e.g., \\wikilink{spells/magic_arrow}{Magic Arrow.}\n"
"\\iftoggle{printable}{%\n"
"  You can find further information about them in the \\pagelink{wiki}{Game Wiki}.\n"
"}{%\n"
"  Clicking them will take you to a Wiki page about the specific card.\\\\\n"
"}\n"
"\\pagelink{Expansion Content}{Expansion Content} from different expansions is marked with colored bars on the left margin:\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\textbf{注意}：在本规则书中，%\n"
"\\textbf{粗体文字}用于提示重要规则。%\n"
"\\textit{斜体文字}用于游戏示例。%\n"
"\\pagelink{Heroes of Might and Magic III}{棕色超链接}会带你前往规则书的其他部分。%\n"
"特定卡牌的名称后会附加一个\\textcolor{goldenbrown}{\\textbf{°}}，例如\\wikilink{spells/magic_arrow}{魔法箭}。%\n"
"\\iftoggle{printable}{%\n"
"  你可以在\\pagelink{wiki}{游戏Wiki}中找到关于它们的更多信息。%\n"
"}{%\n"
"  点击它们会带你前往关于该特定卡牌的Wiki页面。\\\\%\n"
"}\n"
"来自不同扩展的\\pagelink{Expansion Content}{扩展内容}会在左侧页边用彩色条标记：\n"
"\n"

